archimate:DataObject.name: TariffUsageProdOfferPriceCharge
archimate:DataObject.documentation: A specific rate that applies to ProductUsages aggregated during a certain period. For example; all evening minutes are aggregated during one month before being globally rated by a TarifUsageProdOfferPriceCharge 1. And all daytime minutes are aggregated during one month before being globally rated by a TarifUsageProdOfferPriceCharge 2.
